added.title: Magic Man
added.description: In a quest to become a magic man, Beast Boy accidentally destroys Raven's spell book, so they must go find another one.

added.title: Duncan Disorderly
added.description: Duncan escapes during a community walk only to discover he has to babysit Cody and Bridgette.

added.title: Soother or Later
added.description: A terrified Duncan, who's afraid of lightning, learns it's even harder to break back into school than it was to break out when he finally escapes and finds himself in a dark alley with Izzy during a thunderstorm.

added.title: Camping is In Tents
added.description: A class camping trip turns into a treasure hunt while Harold is determined to catch Bigfoot and keep everyone safe.

added.title: Mutt Ado About Owen
added.description: After accidentally hypnotizing Owen into being a dog, Harold thinks he must reverse the hypnosis to avoid going to jail.

added.title: Simons Are Forever
added.description: Duncan and Leshawna try to take advantage of Izzy's love for the game of Simon Says.

added.title: Stop! Hamster Time
added.description: Owen takes over the job of caring for the class hamster and learns that he's evil.

added.title: Driving Miss Crazy
added.description: Duncan leads Beth to believe she's broken his battery-powered bike and makes her chauffeur him around in a wagon for the day as punishment.

added.title: Weiner Takes All
added.description: After forgetting to book a Hot Diggity Doggity Dog mascot on National Hotdog Day, Chef tries to pass off an Australian man dressed as a kangaroo as a substitute.

added.title: Apoca-lice Now
added.description: When Chef brokers a truce with lice by selecting three kids to "host" them on their heads, Courtney instigates a kid vs. lice war.

added.title: Gnome More Mister Nice Guy
added.description: When the daycare gets taken over by evil gnomes, Duncan finds himself on the wrong team.

added.title: It's Story Time
added.description: After the Rustbucket breaks down, Ben, Gwen and Grandpa Max find themselves killing time at the local town library but soon scramble to out maneuver Hex as he searches for a hidden ancient artifact.

added.title: Cosplay Day
added.description: Team Tennyson enjoy the biggest convention in town, but when a gawky costume store employee finds a familiar-looking helmet in the back of the store and tries it on, Ben is faced with the return of an old foe in a new form: Forever Knight!

added.title: Waterfilter
added.description: Ben, Gwen, and Max's trip to Niagara Falls is cut short by the horrid Hydromanders, creatures menacing them and their fellow tourists.

added.title: The Ring Leader
added.description: While winning big on a Sumo Slammers video game, Ben gets the idea to win a wrestling match for real until an intimidating wrestler named Iron Kyle decides to make it a true challenge.

added.title: Riding the Storm Out
added.description: Ben and Gwen's camping trip is interrupted by the emotionless Weatherheads (Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o) but a malfunctioning Omnitrix firing out a mishmash of aliens may not be the forecast for success.

added.title: Pool Duel
added.description: Unikitty and the gang are having a great time at the public pool, until they try to get Puppycorn to swim in the deep end with them. Puppycorn is terrified of the deep end. Now Unikitty and the gang must get him over his fear, so he can have maximum pool fun. Meanwhile, Master Frown and Brock are hatching a plan to ruin everyone's fun, by pulling the pool's plug.

added.title: Rock Friend
added.description: Unikitty discovers Puppycorn's only other friend is a boring old rock. Encouraged to "make more friends," Puppycorn just can't find someone he clicks with, until he takes her advice and decides to literally make a new friend out of the best parts of his friends. This won't go well.

added.title: Kitchen Chaos
added.description: After a workplace injury, Richard is unable to do his servant work. Unikitty and the others take on the task of one simple chore, clean the kitchen. This incredibly boring task taxes our heroes as they find every way possible to not do it. Will they be able to accomplish this goal and bring Richard back?

added.title: Ninja vs. Lava
added.description: The ninja find themselves trapped in a pyramid and must escape encroaching lava to warn NINJAGO City of a new Serpentine invasion.

added.title: Snaketastrophy
added.description: The Serpentine attack on NINJAGO City is seen from an unexpected perspective - entirely in the style of a live newscast delivered by Gayle Gossip and her cameraman.

added.title: Powerless
added.description: The ninja rush to the NINJAGO Museum of History to recover a dangerous scroll before it falls into the hands of the Serpentine Sorceress Aspheera.

added.title: Ancient History
added.description: While Aspheera pursues revenge on the "Treacherous Deceiver" who betrayed her, the ninja make a startling discovery.

added.title: Fright Wig
added.description: When the King cannot overcome his fears, he abuses having the Sheriff's Dept. on call.

added.title: Letras Desastrosas
added.description: La pandilla está planeando una sorpresa para Puppycorn, así que deletrean las cosas cuando hablan para que él no se entere. Desesperado por saber lo que dicen, Puppycorn encuentra un libro mágico que cree que lo ayudará a aprender a deletrear, ipero sin saberlo, el libro le enseña a lanzar hechizos! ¿Se dará cuenta Puppycorn de que el conocimiento es poder, y de que algunos secretos se guardan por una razón?

added.title: Kitty y Halcon: Protectores de la Ley
added.description: Cuando el juguete favorito de Perricornio desaparece, Unikitty y Halcondrilo se unen para localizar al ladrón, ial estilo socios policías! Pero cuando las cosas se ponen difíciles y el caso no se resuelve, ya no es solo su sociedad la que está en juego, sino también su amistad.

added.title: Momento Perfecto
added.description: Cuando Halcondrilo admite su amor por la Dra. Fox, Unikitty y sus amigos se convierten en sus gurús del amor para ayudarlo a confesar sus sentimientos por ella. Por desgracia, los grandes planes de Unikitty para el momento perfecto del amor lo complican todo.

added.title: Brawler Headhunting/Lightning's Entrance Exam
added.description: Brawler Headhunting: As acting president of Kazami International, Shun is called upon to entertain another new young CEO Luca Schmidt, who's interested in doing business with the Kazami International. But Shun quickly realizes something is up when Luca tries woo him over to his brawling team - the Glanz Five. /Lightning's Entrance Exam: The Awesome Brawlers may be world famous heroes, but that doesn't mean they get out of going to school. They are still regular kids, doing regular kid things. But teachers may have something to say when Lightening decides he wants to join his buddies in the classroom.

added.title: Duelo en la Piscina
added.description: Unikitty y la pandilla se están divirtiendo mucho en la piscina pública, hasta que intentan que Perricornio nade en la parte profunda con ellos. A Perricornio le da muchísimo miedo ir a lo más profundo. Ahora Unikitty y la banda deben ayudarlo a superar su miedo para que se divierta al máximo en la piscina. Mientras tanto, Master Frown y Brock están tramando un plan para arruinar la diversión de todos: quitar el tapón de la piscina. Ahora Perricornio debe dominar su miedo para detener a los que quieren estropear la diversión.

added.title: Filtro Acuatico
added.description: El viaje de Ben, Gwen y Max a las Cataratas del Niágara se ve interrumpido por los horribles Hydromanders: unas criaturas que los amenazan a ellos y a los demás turistas.

added.title: El Lider Del Ring
added.description: Cuando Ben tiene una racha ganadora en un videojuego, se le ocurre una idea para ganar un partido real de lucha, hasta que un luchador intimidante decide convertirlo en un verdadero desafío.

added.title: Sobreviviendo A La Tormenta
added.description: El campamento de Ben y Gwen se ve interrumpido por los gélidos Weatherheads -Gust-o, Hail-o, & Shock-o-, pero un Omnitrix que funciona mal y dispara un montón de extraterrestres podría no ser un pronóstico de éxito.

added.title: Ninja Contra Lava
added.description: Los ninja se encuentran atrapados en una pirámide y deben escapar de la lava invasora para advertir a la ciudad de NINJAGO de una nueva invasión serpentina.

added.title: Amigo roca
added.description: Unikitty descubre que el único otro amigo de Puppycorn es una roca vieja y aburrida. Incentivado a ""hacer más amigos"", Puppycorn no puede encontrar a alguien con quien sienta afinidad, hasta que sigue el consejo de Unikitty y decide literalmente hacer un nuevo amigo con las mejores partes de sus amigos. Esto no irá bien.

added.title: Caos en la cocina
added.description: Después de lesionarse en su lugar de trabajo, Richard no puede hacer sus tareas de criado. Unikitty y los demás se encargan de una simple tarea: limpiar la cocina. Esta actividad increíblemente aburrida es un desafío para nuestros héroes, que buscan todas las formas posibles de no hacerla. ¿Serán capaces de alcanzar esta meta y traer de regreso a Richard?

added.title: Serpientastrofe
added.description: El ataque de Serpentine en NINJAGO City se ve desde una perspectiva inesperada, completamente al estilo de un noticiero en vivo entregado por Gayle Gossip y su camarógrafo.

removed.title: Baost in Show
removed.description: When Bao Bao returns, and the King makes him his pet, Mao Mao must rescue his ex-partner.

removed.title: Te Quiero Mao Mao
removed.description: Un solitario explosivo y su mejor amigo holgazán se desvían del viaje que los llevará a convertirse en leyenda y descubren que su historia apenas comienza.

removed.title: Historia Antigua
removed.description: Mientras Aspheera busca vengarse del "Engañador Traicionero" que la traicionó, el ninja hace un sorprendente descubrimiento.

removed.title: Impotente
removed.description: El ninja corre al Museo de Historia de NINJAGO para recuperar un pergamino peligroso antes de que caiga en manos de la Hechicera Serpentina Aspheera.

removed.title: Rain on Your Wedding Day
removed.description: While facing off with The Brain, Robin tries to teach the other Titans the proper definition of irony.

removed.title: Tales from the Omnitrix
removed.description: Team Tennyson trade campfire stories in an anthology-style series that pits Ben against his archrival, Kevin 11, and teaches our hero the power of imagination.

removed.title: Bottomless Ben
removed.description: While visiting Carlsbad Caverns National Park, the Tennyson's come across the "Bottomless Pit", a naturally formed pit with no bottom. Ben fights his better judgment to jump in the pit and be the first person to find the bottom, until Kevin 11 shows up and starts to goad Ben into a contest to the bottom of the pit! The natural rivalry is put on hold, however, with the arrival of Breaker One-Nine, who has come to destroy the Caverns!

removed.title: Take 10
removed.description: While trying to film his own indie film, Ben accidentally allows the Bug Gang to go free and when he takes the fight to their hidden lair Ben has to take on their narcissistic leader, the Ant Queen.

removed.title: The Clocktopus
removed.description: In a peaceful coastal town, Ben must not only face the archaic antagonist Steam Smythe and his latest creation, the Clocktopus, but also his deepest, darkest fear: Squids!

removed.title: Growing Pains
removed.description: During a stop at the superstore Shoppë, Ben and Gwen are transformed into babies by nanny-gone-nuts Nanny Nightmare, who will stop at nothing to reshape the world in the image of her daycare.

removed.title: Perfect Moment
removed.description: When Hawkodile admits his love for Dr. Fox, Unikitty and the gang become his love gurus to help him confess his feelings for her. Unfortunately, Unikitty's grand plans for the perfect moment of love complicates everything.

removed.title: Kitty & Hawk
removed.description: When Puppycorn's favorite toy goes missing, Unikitty & Hawkodile team up to track down the thief, buddy-cop style! But when things get tough and the case goes cold, now it's not just their partnership on the line, but their friendship!

removed.title: This Spells Disaster
removed.description: The gang is planning a surprise for Puppycorn, so they spell things out when talking so he won't find out. Desperate to know what they're saying, Puppycorn finds a magic book that he thinks will help him learn to spell, but unbeknownst to him, it's teaching him how to cast spells! Will Puppycorn realize that knowledge is power and some secrets are kept for a reason?

removed.title: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call/Phantom Thief Ajit
removed.description: The Phantom Thief Comes to Call: An archeological discovery is made in Los Volmos. Exploration at the site is cut short, when a master thief and his apprentice attempt to steal the ancient Bakugan artifacts. When the Awesome Brawlers hear the news, they step in to thwart the thieves./Phantom Thief Ajit: An Ancient Bakugon artifact from an archeological discovery is placed in the Los Volmos Museum. The Awesome Brawlers are charged with guarding the artifacts from any further attempts thievery.

removed.title: Sleeper Sofa
removed.description: When the Sky Pirates infiltrate Sheriff HQ, they put our heroes in danger!

removed.title: I Love You Mao Mao
removed.description: An explosive loner and his slacker best friend are waylaid from their journey into legend, only to find that their story is just beginning.
